Frequently Asked Questions for Third Point Reinsurance (NYSE:TPRE)
What is Third Point Reinsurance's stock symbol?

Third Point Reinsurance trades on the New York Stock Exchange (NYSE) under the ticker symbol "TPRE."



How were Third Point Reinsurance's earnings last quarter?

Third Point Reinsurance Ltd. (NYSE:TPRE) posted its earnings results on Thursday, November, 3rd. The company reported $0.68 earnings per share for the quarter, topping the Thomson Reuters' consensus estimate of $0.58 by $0.10. The firm had revenue of $216.54 million for the quarter, compared to analyst estimates of $158.35 million. Third Point Reinsurance had a return on equity of 12.53% and a net margin of 21.30%.  View Third Point Reinsurance's Earnings History.



When will Third Point Reinsurance make its next earnings announcement?

Third Point Reinsurance is scheduled to release their next quarterly earnings announcement on Wednesday, August, 2nd 2017. View Earnings Estimates for Third Point Reinsurance.



